3'-Sulfonylesters of 2,5'-anhydro-1-(2-deoxy-beta-d-threo-pentofuranosyl)thymine as precursors for the synthesis of [(18)F]FLT: syntheses and radiofluorination trials. Title compounds [3'-sulfonylesters of 2,5'-anhydro-1-(2-deoxy-beta-d-threo-pentofuranosyl)thymine: 2,5'-anhydro-1-(2-deoxy-3-methanesulfonyl-beta-d-threo-pentofuranosyl)thymine (1a) 2,5'-anhydro-1-(2-deoxy-3-(4-nitrobenzenesulfonyl)-beta-d-threo-pentofuranosyl)thymine (1b)